title: Your Excuses Suck!
itunes:title: Your Excuses Suck!
description:
Episode 376 - Excuses are like buttholes, everyone has one and they all stink! Your life will not change until you learn how to finally release yourself from your excuses. In this episode I teach how to free yourself from your excuses and take extreme ownership of your life.
